</tr>
<tr>
<td>Cash discount</td>
<td>-10.50</td>
<td>0.00</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
<p>The overpayment amount of 0.50 will remain as an open balance on the payment and can be settled against another invoice. The following accounting entries are generated for the payment and the settlement. <strong>Payment</strong></p>
