<td>94.50</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
<p>The customer submits a payment for 95.00 within the cash discount date. The payment is settled against the invoice for 105.00. After the invoice and payment are settled, the following transactions are created for the customer in Accounts receivable.</p>
<table>
